    public interface Operation<RESPONSE_TYPE>
    An operation, synchronous or asynchronous, optionally used to define requests.

      Timer getTimer()
      Returns the Timer used to track the performance of this Request instance.

    • Method Detail

      • getTimer

        Timer getTimer()
        Returns the Timer used to track the performance of this Request instance. Null is not allowed as return value, but Timer.NOP can be used to disable tracking.
        Returns:
        the Timer used to track the performance of this Request instance.
